Memory map
==========
OpenRISC:
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| Range                   | Description                   |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0x00000000 - 0x3fffffff | FPGA DDR3 SDRAM               |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0x40000000 - 0x7fffffff | HPS DDR3 SDRAM                |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0x90000000 - 0x90000020 | UART0                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0x91000000 - 0x91000001 | GPIO0                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0x96000000 - 0x964fffff | DIILA                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+

ARM (only shared resources shown):
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| Range                   | Description                   |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0x00000000 - 0x3fffffff | HPS DDR3 SDRAM                |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0xc0000000 - 0xfbffffff | FPGA DDR3 SDRAM (first 960MB) |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0xff320000 - 0xff320020 | UART0                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0xff322000 - 0xff322001 | GPIO0                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
| 0xff32c000 - 0xff32dfff | DIILA                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------+
